==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Fructify
<hw>Fruc"ti*fy</hw>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <vmorph>[<pos>imp. & p. p.</pos>
<conjf>Fructified</conjf> <pr>(?)</pr>; <pos>p. pr. & vb. n.</pos>
